{"tid":2215772,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"714新城市廣場衝突 胡雅文判兩被告四年 一被告3年4個月","createTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T09:15:48.000Z","uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3df96c9db24fc6aab1c3b519e50e927e7b72cc9e","tid":2215772,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"#區域法院第廿八庭<br />\n#胡雅文法官<br />\n#判刑<br />\n#0714沙田<br />\n<br />\n梁 (24) 已還押30天<br />\n龔 (51) 已還押20天<br />\n李 (17) 已還押20天<br />\n<br />\n兩項暴動罪<br />\n<br />\n控罪詳情：2019年7月14日在沙田新城市廣場，首被告以及第2被告各參與2次暴動，而第3被告參與1次暴動<br />\n<br />\n答辯詳情<br />\n<br />\n📌判刑理由：<br />\n（詳情後補）<br />\n<br />\n速報：<br />\n梁 合共判處4年監禁<br />\n龔 合共判處4年監禁<br />\n李 判處3年又4個月監禁"},{"pid":"9288f4a58f72763e5a67dd8e673cf8570464df5c","tid":2215772,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9780&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=3023264c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9780</a>"},{"pid":"9f68a03440b85accc90d370cf9eb1421dd97c0f5","tid":2215772,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"4年，點解條臭閪乜鳩判4年"},{"pid":"664293b6d4b5d19dfa3b52631c7623879071c69e","tid":2215772,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f68a03440b85accc90d370cf9eb1421dd97c0f5","tid":2215772,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"4年，點解條臭閪乜鳩判4年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"次次都6年量刑起點，認罪扣三分一，之後求情嗰啲唔扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb91b9aaeff7388a35b4be1299a402cc4d3b00b","tid":2215772,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:09:14.000Z","msg":"四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"